metadata.name: Forbice - Prologue
metadata.description:
“Forbice” (Scissors) was born as a song. In fact, it comes from the need to revive sound pieces ripped from oblivion of a Hard Disk found. Several steps, several rebirths, ultimately as NFT. This is how things went. Obviously, nothing stays the same and no idea stays true to itself for more than one Moon.
